text: Hii Abha, Abhi  to muje bas ye yaad aara hai ki hum mandir gaye the, humne maje kiye the, tera bday bhi manaya tha. Tera room kaafi organised tha, par humne sab ulta pulta kar diya tha. Mast hai yr tu, aise hi padhte rehna, drawing krte rehna, aur cake khila dena kabhi to. Anyway kaafi maja aaya, And nanital reh gaya tha vo bhi dekhna hai.
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Aur bajaj bhaiya kaise ho, first year se hi pata tha ki terko hi banana hai room mate to. Ek dum mast chill banda. Ek praani ne koshish ki thi ki naa bane. Maje aaye yr saath me, fest me kaam, hall 10 jaana, ground jaana, ncl cc me jaga rokna, canteen me match dekhna, tere ghar jaake, placement me tera rona, aur vo to hai hi all time tuje chidhane me.  Ok to maine likh diya ab tu bhi likh dio
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Komal bhaiiii, tere naam ka kya kya nhi kiya tha maine. Merko aisa yaad hai apan kaafi ache dost the, fir dost reh gaye, fir ab oracle jaake ache dost banna hai. Muje yaad hai bmid me tere room me aake kitna pareshan krta tha tuje, south ke baare me poochta rehta tha. Tune ek kaafi achi cheej bhi samjhayi thi muje, shayad tuje yaad bhi na ho. Kaise batti ke course me dono ki haalat kharab rehti thi, par anyway dono ne kuch na kuch kar hi liya. Kaafi sahi hai yr tu, kitna shaant lagta hai. Bangalore me machayege DiKER
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Deepak bro, teri vo the story of my life vaali bakchodi hai mere paas. Second year summers, RM, CCD, Messenger pe gand machana, GYM. Mast banda hai yrr tu. Ekdum chilll. Apan milte to alag sa mohol banjata tha, mess me aapke darshan ho jaate the.  Milte hai ab party sharty krni hai.

text: Hi shunal karma from hall 3, originally from kotha(rajasthan). Muje to yaad hi nhi ki terse kab kaise baat cheet shuru hui thi (maybe ache dosto me aisa hi hota hai yaad nhi hona chahiye), shayad badminton ya fir class kyuki aur kahi to tu jaata nhi tha. Shareef bacha hai yr tu. Saari cheeje ek taraf, aur rm me lift ke saamne vale sofe pe stand up ka maja ek taraf, kya alag level hass raha tha tu. Ok to aur kuch likhna senti krne vali baat hojegi, isliye bas.
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Hello first year roomie. Bhai tere me to zameen aasmaan ka farak aaya hai. Pehle light jlti nhi thi, aur end me band nhi hoti thi. Tere raat ke rituals kaafi stylish hai, boroline ki lipstick lagana, jhaadu lagana aur Dhanish ki lena. Ankur aur sudhanshu ke UP ke charche sunne me bhi maja aata tha. Teri GPL ki video padi hai bhai, kya alag level thi kishan aur ankur aur dalle ne zyada maara tha, mai to bas khada tha. Badminton bhi khele kaafi, aur csgo me vo NEPAAALI vaala to bakchodh tha. Yrr japan to muje bhi jaane ka mann tha, par kisi aur kaam se. Milte hai kabhi. Maje maaro.
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Dash bhai, ultimate lab partner hai tu, jisko sab kuch aata hai. Bhai tu sach me kaafi hardworking hai. Yaad hai tu merko lab ke baad apni intern ka batara tha ki aakhiri me cancel ho gyi, aur maine bola tha ki bhai badia hoga. Aur summer me hua bhi. Are apan TA project me bhi saath the, kya fraud maara tha, aur maine perfect wheels banaye the. Lab chahe jitni bhi faaltu kyu na ho, par maje poore aaye the. Bhai bas aise hi chaapte rehna aur maje maarte rehna. Milte hai kbhi to.
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Hello bhai, tu to merko bas aise hi chalte firte milta tha. EK baar ccd me mila tha yaad hai, steve jobs vali book ke baare me batara tha. Maje maarna bhai aur milte hai kbhi!!
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik

text: Bhaiya me bhaiya sudhanshu bhaiya. Allahad ke chacha se 20 gaddhe mangvadena aur scooter dheere chalan ki fatte na. Bhai apan ne wing me gand macha ke rakhte the. Mess me saksham se gaalion ka game. Wing me sagnik ki lena. Thermo ki class ke vaqt ccd jaana, quiz chod dena. Bhai apan kaafi courses me saath the, tu kishan aur first year mai  library bhi jaate the. Bhai teri best quality story sunana  hai matlab itna bakchodh mirch masale ke saath story batata hai, sach me master(shayd tera nick name) hai. Kolkata vaali to epic thiiiiiiiii. Aise hi maje karo, acad to sambhal hi leta hai tu. Milte hai kisi din, fir koi badia si cheej sunana.
author: Sparsh  Kaoshik
